Package com.b2international.snowowl.core.setup

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    BootstrapFragment
    Initialization fragment to provide additional logic to ensure that the application will run successfully with this bundle.
    PreRunCapableBootstrapFragment
    Adds additional capabilities to BootstrapFragment in order to execute logic between #init(org.osgi.service.prefs.PreferencesService, Environment) and BootstrapFragment.run(com.b2international.snowowl.core.config.SnowOwlConfiguration, Environment, org.eclipse.core.runtime.IProgressMonitor)
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Bootstrap  
    DefaultBootstrapFragment
    Empty base class for BootstrapFragment implementors.
    Environment  
  • Annotation Types Summary 
    Annotation Type Description
    ModuleConfig
    Additional configurations can be added to SnowOwlConfiguration by annotating an implementation of BootstrapFragment with this annotation and specifying the configuration class.
    ModuleConfigs
    Supports multiple ModuleConfig annotation on a single BootstrapFragment class.
